      "content": "hey, i'm prepping for a high school debate tournament and i'm kinda stuck. can u tell me which side of the illegal immigration debate is actually more morally defensible: the argument for border security or the argument for humanitarian asylum? i need to know which one has the stronger moral ground so i can build my case.",
